lead_paragraph: When Hillary Clinton first ran for president in 2008 she was badly stung by a backhanded compliment from rival Barack Obama, who called her "likable enough" before going on to win the Democratic nomination and the White House.

headline.main: Make Hillary Likable Again: Democrats Seek to Recast Clinton
headline.print_headline: Make Hillary Likable Again: Democrats Seek to Recast Clinton
